          <title>Americans' pride in U.S. history and democracy drops, and fewer are proud to be American, polls find</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A new AP-NORC poll finds that Americans have grown less proud of the country’s history or the way its democracy works over the past several years. That includes Americans' pride in the nation’s military and its political influence around the globe.]]></description>
