          <title>Minneapolis City Council votes to repeal bathhouse ban</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Bathhouses were banned in the city in 1988 during the AIDS epidemic. The Minneapolis City Council voted on Thursday to repeal the ban. It now heads to Mayor Jacob Frey.]]></description>
